      "value": "<p>Beginning at 6th level, the guardian spirits that aid you can provide supernatural protection to those you defend. If you are @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.gaVd6MJT8Q6PLE9B]{Raging} and a creature you can see within 30 feet of you takes damage, you can use your reaction to reduce that damage by <strong>2d6</strong>.</p>\n<p>When you reach certain levels in this class, you can reduce the damage by more: by <strong>3d6 </strong>at 10th level and by <strong>4d6 </strong>at 14th level.</p>",
